I cannot allow that. \n< Serena >
Hmm. Do you have a purpose? \n< Cecilia >

Ah, Unicorn, right? You can do it. \n< Cecilia >
Why? \n< Serena >
Oh! \n< Serena >
I see. That's how it is... \n< Cecilia >
I do not like this kind of behavior. \n< Serena >
Oh, really? But just from that simple conversation, I
was able to discover two important pieces of
information. \n< Cecilia >
One of the rumors that seems quite plausible is that a
unicorn has been brought into this town. \n< Cecilia >
The other thing is that your purpose is the Unicorn. \n< Cecilia >
So. What good does knowing that do? \n< Serena >
Well, this information alone won't be enough to sell,
you know. \n< Cecilia >
Something for sale...? \n< Serena >
Oh... come to think of it, I haven't introduced myself
yet. \n< Cecilia >
Nice to meet you. I am Cecilia. Cecilia Valladon. \n< Cecilia >
I'm working as an informant. Can I count on you for
work, Serena? \n< Cecilia >
(Okay? My next job is to expose Goupil's fraudulent
accumulation of wealth.) \n< Cecilia >
I'll break into the mansion and find the evidence. I
want you to be my support. \n< Cecilia >
(To be specific, I want you to infiltrate their
mansion as a maid.) \n< Cecilia >
(There are three things I want you to do.) \n< Cecilia >
(The first thing is to leave the key to the bathroom
window open. I will infiltrate from there.) \n< Cecilia >
(The second is to halt the nightly patrols.) \n< Cecilia >
(The third one is tomorrow morning. I will escape from
the second floor, so I need to cause a commotion on
the first floor to attract attention.) \n< Cecilia >
(It's an easy job, right?) \n< Cecilia >

... \n< Cecilia >

... \n< Cecilia >

\n< Serena >

Face... \n< Serena >

interest to snitch on that Goupil guy. \n< Cecilia >

are as otherworldly as a Unicorn, came before me so
easily. \n< Cecilia >
It just hit me. I had a feeling about this and it
turned out to be spot on. \n< Cecilia >
So, if your secret is found out, you can't normally
refuse a job. You don't know what might happen to you. \n< Cecilia >
I also would have been in trouble if you had escaped,
you know? Well, that kind of trouble was unexpected
though. \n< Cecilia >
\n< Serena >
Um... well... \n< Cecilia >
Is my appeal still not enough? \n< Cecilia >
\n< Serena >
Don't you have a job you want to entrust to me? This
capable information broker, Cecilia, is here for you. \n< Cecilia >
Very well. I certainly want to ask for your
assistance. You are the one I've been searching for. \n< Serena >
Information broker Lady Cecilia Valladon. Please find
my Unicorn, Splendor. \n< Serena >
Yeah, that's right. We gotta do it like that. \n< Cecilia >
Thanks for coming. \n< Cecilia >
